        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Public Service Retirement Fairness Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill expands the ability of 403(b) retirement plans (i.e., retirement plans designed for certain employees of public schools, nonprofits, and churches) to invest in collective investment trusts, which are a group of pooled investment assets held by a bank or trust company.</p>]]>
        </text>
